Mantlebio SDK#

Overview#

Mantle SDK is a comprehensive SDK designed to help developers leverage data within Mantle’s platform.

For more information on the Mantle platform, visit Mantle’s website.

For more examples on Mantle SDK, visit Mantle’s documentation.

Getting Started#

Install via pip:

pip install mantlebio

For more information see the Installation page of our documentation.
